You can define a custom function to be used as your metric, it have to follow this pattern (take 3 arguments):
```
def l1_norm(prediction, target, inputs):
    return tf.reduce_sum(tf.abs(prediction - target))
net = tflearn.regression(net, metric=l1_norm)
